---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - Lemon: Your Nutrition Partner" 
  description="Privacy Policy for Lemon: Your Nutrition Partner app by CODALITY S.R.L."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-white">
    <!-- Navigation back to main site -->
    <nav class="bg-white border-b border-gray-100 px-6 py-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
          </svg>
          Back to Lemon
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main content -->
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
      <header class="mb-12 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          <span class="gradient-text">Privacy Policy</span> for Lemon: Your Nutrition Partner
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          This Privacy Policy explains how CODALITY S.R.L. collects, uses, stores, and protects your information when you use our app.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
          <strong>Effective Date:</strong> February 14th, 2025
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-lemon p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-lg">
          <p class="text-gray-800 mb-0">
            By downloading or using the App, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with our practices, please do not use the App.
          </p>
        </div>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">1. Data Collection & Use</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">1.1 Personal Data</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Authentication & Account Information:</strong> When you create an account, we require an email address and password for authentication. No additional personal details (such as your name, age, or gender) are collected. In addition, the App collects a device identifier to help manage and secure your account.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">1.2 Health & Nutrition Data</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Local Storage for Calculations:</strong> The App allows you to log food intake, manage recipes, and track meal plans and macronutrients. All such data remains stored locally on your device and is used solely to calculate and display your macro goals. No sensitive health data is transmitted or stored on our servers.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">1.3 Usage Data</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Analytics & Improvement:</strong> We use Firebase Analytics to track app interactions, screen views, and error reports. This usage data is collected to help us improve the functionality and user experience of the App over time.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">2. Data Storage & Security</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">2.1 Storage Locations</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Local and Cloud Storage:</strong> Most of your data (e.g., journal entries, recipes, meal plans) is stored locally on your device. The only information stored on our servers is your email address (via Firebase) and data related to crash reports and feedback (via Bugfender).
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">2.2 Security Measures</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Data Protection:</strong> We employ industry-standard security measures including encryption and secure network connections to safeguard your data. While we take reasonable steps to protect your information, please note that no security system is completely foolproof. In the event of a data breach, we will follow our internal breach-response procedures and notify you as required by applicable law.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">3. Data Sharing & Third Parties</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">3.1 Third-Party Services</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Analytics and Feedback Providers:</strong> To operate the App effectively, we share minimal information (such as your email address for authentication and device identifiers) with trusted third parties:
                <ul class="mt-2 ml-4 space-y-1">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-2"></span>
                    <strong>Firebase:</strong> For user authentication and usage analytics.
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-2"></span>
                    <strong>Bugfender:</strong> For collecting crash reports and user feedback.
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-2"></span>
                    <strong>OpenAI:</strong> To generate nutritional data and recipe suggestions (note that the names of your food collections may be sent to OpenAI for helping allocate a generated recipe in an existing collection).
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">3.2 APIs & Integrations</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Secure Integrations:</strong> Any integrations or APIs used within the App (for example, for analytics or feedback collection) are selected and managed with security in mind. We do not share personal or sensitive data beyond what is necessary for these services.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">4. User Rights & Data Management</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">4.1 Access, Review, and Deletion</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>User Control:</strong> You can access and review your data directly through the App. In addition, a delete account function is provided, which ensures that your personal data and associated information (stored with Firebase and Bugfender) are removed from our systems upon your request.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">4.2 Consent for Data Collection</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Opt-In for Analytics:</strong> During account creation, you are asked for consent to share your data for analytics purposes. You may adjust your consent settings through the App at any time.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">4.3 Age and Consent</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Compliance with Regulations:</strong> By using the App, you confirm that you have the legal capacity to consent to the processing of your data. As a Romanian entity, we comply with the GDPR requirements for data processing and protection.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">5. Data Retention & Updates</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">5.1 Data Retention</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Retention Policy:</strong> We retain your data only as long as necessary to provide you with the App's services. Should you request deletion of your account, your data will be removed. Please note that while we delete data from our systems, the retention practices of third-party services like Firebase may be governed by their respective policies.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">5.2 Policy Changes</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Notification of Updates:</strong> If we make changes to this Privacy Policy, we will notify you through in-app notifications and via email. Continued use of the App after any changes signifies your acceptance of the updated policy.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">6. Data Sent to OpenAI</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">6.1 AI-Powered Recipe Creation</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Data Processing for AI Features:</strong> When you use our AI-powered recipe or dish creation feature, we send a prompt to OpenAI. This prompt includes only a general description of the desired output structure and any specific text or image you provide.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">6.2 No Personal Data Transmission</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Strict Data Minimization:</strong> We do not send any personal data to OpenAI. This means no name, email, user ID, location, or health-related information is included. Only the information necessary to generate a recipe or dish or macro nutrients for a food item is transmitted, and this data is processed on a temporary basis.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">7. Purpose of Data Processing</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The primary purpose of collecting and processing your data is to:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              Authenticate and manage your account securely.
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              Enable and enhance the nutritional tracking features of the App.
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              Analyze app usage to continuously improve the service.
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              Generate recipes, dishes, macro nutrients estimations, through our AI-powered features without compromising your personal information.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">8. OpenAI's Privacy Practices</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            While we do not store or access the data once it is sent to OpenAI, please be aware that OpenAI may have its own data retention and privacy practices. For more details on how OpenAI handles data, please review <a href="https://openai.com/privacy" class="text-lemon hover:text-lemon-dark underline">OpenAI's Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">9. Additional Considerations</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">9.1 International Compliance</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>GDPR Adherence:</strong> As an entity based in Romania, we adhere to the GDPR regulations. While we are not certain if we are subject to the CCPA, we strive to meet the highest standards of data protection and privacy.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">9.2 Marketing & Communications</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-2 h-2 bg-lemon rounded-full mt-2.5 mr-3"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Opt-In Communications:</strong> With your consent during sign-up, we may use your email address for marketing communications. You can opt out of these communications at any time through the settings provided in the App.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">10. Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your personal data, please contact our support team at:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-gray-800 mb-2">
              <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@lemonnutrition.eu" class="text-lemon hover:text-lemon-dark underline">support@lemonnutrition.eu</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="bg-lemon/10 border border-lemon/20 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-gray-800 mb-0">
            By using "Lemon: Your Nutrition Partner," you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms. We reserve the right to update this policy at any time, and we will provide notification of any significant changes as described above.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 px-6 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="flex justify-center space-x-8 mb-4">
          <a href="/legal/privacy-policy" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 font-medium">Privacy Policy</a>
          <a href="/legal/terms-and-conditions" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 font-medium">Terms & Conditions</a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          © 2025 CODALITY S.R.L. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F7C720 0%, #E5B91A 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }
  
  .bg-lemon {
    background-color: #F7C720;
  }
  
  .text-lemon {
    color: #F7C720;
  }
  
  .hover\:text-lemon-dark:hover {
    color: #E5B91A;
  }
  
  .border-lemon {
    border-color: #F7C720;
  }
  
  .bg-lemon\/10 {
    background-color: rgba(247, 199, 32, 0.1);
  }
  
  .border-lemon\/20 {
    border-color: rgba(247, 199, 32, 0.2);
  }
</style> 